data.description: Welcome home to this IMMACULATE 4 Bedroom, 3.5 Bath, 2 story! Pride of ownership shows the second you walk into the front door. The main level features a formal dining room (would also make a perfect rec room), updated kitchen with stainless appliances, pantry, new countertops, backsplash and flooring. The living room leads out to the beautiful, heated, 4 seasons room & the breakfast nook leads out to the deck that overlooks the fenced backyard. Main floor laundry room with washer, dryer, & sink. The upper level is unique with 2 master suites and 2 other bedrooms. The larger MBR has a full bath with a vaulted ceiling, skylight, whirlpool tub, double sink and 2 walk in closets. The garage is finished and heated and has attic storage. This home has had many recent updates, some include: New siding, gutters, downspouts, newer HVAC, freshly painted interior, new carpet & vinyl plank flooring, too many to mention, please ask your agent for the list of all improvements in agent documents.
